task.summary:
First working version!
Not yet set up correctly for pub but almost there.

- Fix an issue where null backgroundColor in appBar caused a white back button - Fix an issue where calling `Navigator.pop` methods inside `onSubmit` caused NPEs - Add support for controller in the TextField (as a `controller` property in the constructor of `SearchBar`) Versions 1.0.1 - 1.0.4
Update readme to have a screenshots section -- will add on web github since images are being dumb here.
